Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.27,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:14.96,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: sweat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:18.55,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What is that? I had no idea that I have that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:22.72,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was in the lower section of the third drawer of your desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.89,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hidden under a study book cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.40,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello? Did something happen? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:32.69,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.03,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll forgive you if you burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:39.12,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a sec. Punishing and forgiving aren't the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:40.91,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay then, I won't forgive you even if you burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:43.33,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have to burn it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:50.13,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So what are you doing here this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:52.42,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:55.92,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't that the Kisaragi Grand Park's premium entrance ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:54.00,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: Shouko's View
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.61,0:02:57.32,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: Yuuji's View
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.92,0:02:57.34,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you have this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.76,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A nice person gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:04.68,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The only person I know who had this is Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:08.27,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Special Wedding Experience Event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.48,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hello, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.90,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:17.78,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? What? Who are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:19.24,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go then, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.66,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.24,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I never agreed to going.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:27.25,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You promised me that if you lost to me in the Summoned Being Exam War, you'd go out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:29.21,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've long forgotten that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.54,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then you can choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:34.30,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You promised that if you break the promise we'd immediately get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.42,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The details of the promise just completely changed, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.85,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn it! Akihisa, that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.60,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're definitely going to regret th—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:47.02,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All couples hold hands with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:51.06,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you're the only one who locks the joints to prevent escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:55.82,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Welcome to Kisaragi Grand Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:06.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Akihisa, it looks like you're enjoying yourself, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.25,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:09.91,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've got the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:11.88,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why the hell are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.01,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're here too, Hideyoshi. What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:22.34,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.97,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm an employee at the Kisaragi Grand Park;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.64,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have nothing to do with whoever it is you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.23,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you want to keep faking it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.28,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah! My hand slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.11,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Was that necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.95,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you have the tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:43.45,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:47.70,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the Special Premium ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}Alpha to Bravo. Target?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.62,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}Kouta, shift to Wedding mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.21,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\an8}We must bring him down without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.38,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what's with that suspicious phone call?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:58.50,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.59,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's nothing you need to concern yourself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.17,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's pretty clear that it's about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:06.10,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's move on to the special{} commemorative photographs service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.60,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.39,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shouko, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:18.94,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Long term habits are hard to break, aren't they? Ninja Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.95,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, you pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:26.53,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't do it again. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.16,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll continue in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just said I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:33.12,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't have any interest in your panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.71,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This... I can't forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.96,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It hurts... My temples...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.55,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.01,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cheese.
