Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.18,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What kind of picture is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.51,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the special border that our service provides.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:53.73,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This photograph will be placed in the park's photo {}gallery as a commemoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.44,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you guys crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.19,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, are you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:59.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really can't tell what's embarrassing about this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.49,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, look, Ryuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.53,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's have them take a picture of us too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.24,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good thinking, Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:08.99,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey onii-chan, take a picture of us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.45,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm very sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.83,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but this service is only for those who hold premium tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:15.67,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:17.38,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, it's just one picture;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.09,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}we're customers here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:24.59,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Compared to that boring brat, I'm much more suitable for advertisements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:31.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right. Ryuta is a hundred times more handsome than that loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:35.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:38.02,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those people said bad things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.40,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just ignore that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.86,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:44.49,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spare me your crap and just take a picture of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:48.41,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I understand. If you insist, then please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.66,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay! Please put your hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.91,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Very good. Now squeeze as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.08,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.08,Baka While,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.75,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bastards, what the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.50,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You said that you wanted a similar picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:04.55,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You wanna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.17,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap! Hamburger Head is mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.22,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't look down on me, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:14.02,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do I get the feeling that things will become even more of a drag?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:22.73,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How the hell did those three get in here anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.07,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, are you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.28,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What kind of man gets embarrassed just because his{} joints are locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But all couples hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:32.24,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In what way does this position make us look like we're a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:35.66,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey! The sweet, adorable couple over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.37,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look. It thinks so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.21,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's pretty obvious that this guy isn't normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:46.05,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hi, Phi the Fox here to introduce you guys to a very interesting attraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.34,0:07:50.34,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Akihisa was asked out by a college girl a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:54.22,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? Yoshii-kun? Where did you see him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.81,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you here working part-time, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:06.69,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hi, Phi the Fox here to introduce you guys to a very interesting attraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.15,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go ahead, if you want to play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.28,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell me where you recommend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:16.45,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay! Phi recommends the Haunted House you see over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:20.71,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so? Shouko, let's go anywhere but the Haunted House.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.67,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please wait! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.84,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys probably placed traps there to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:32.26,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I beg you, please go to the haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.72,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.85,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's as far as you'll go, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:38.47,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you dare upset Phi, I, Noin, will definitely make you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.98,0:08:41.98,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong, Akihisa? What's with your retarded head?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How rude! There's nothing wrong with my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:47.48,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, it's because Noin-chan is a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.40,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no klutzy fox that would put his head backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:53.57,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yoshii-kun, you put it on backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh crap! No wonder I couldn't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:59.50,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't fix it right now, Sakamoto-kun will see through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:02.42,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do these idiots still think I haven't realized yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:08.25,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, Akihisa, what happened to the date with the college girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:08.88,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:15.26,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yoshii-kun, I heard you were fooling around with other girls
