Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.67,Text Message,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(143,64)\c&HAF73E9&\alpha&H10&\be1}Mizuki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.67,Text Message,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(498,73)\c&H4581EF&\alpha&H10&\be1}Minami
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.50,0:09:21.67,Text Message,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,336)\be3\blur1}RECEIVING
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.52,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What are you talking about, Himeji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{Mizuki - - - Akihisa; receiving}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:24.23,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Minami-chan says she's coming too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please explain to us what the heck is going on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:30.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't spill blood in a happy amusement park...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:34.24,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What the hell is going on, Aki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:42.54,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let us hear your thorough explanation, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.71,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to be completely honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.92,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.71,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hurry, Shouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.26,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's go somewhere{,} other than the Haunted House.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.26,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh? Shouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.35,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're going to the Haunted House.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.23,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hideyoshi, what the hell did you whisper to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.52,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We can hug all we want in the Haunted House.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:25.74,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: Hell's Hospital of Fear!! Haunted House
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.15,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please sign this before you go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.11,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.70,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:21.08,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A contract needs to be signed in order to enter any dangerous attractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:23.91,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it really that dangerous in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.91,0:10:25.75,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But I guess it'll be interesting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.33,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's see... Contract:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:32.84,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I, Sakamoto Yuuji, take Kirishima Shouko as my lawful wife, to have and to hold, from this day forward, for better
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.88,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}or for worse, until death do us part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.13,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here's a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.47,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And here's your official stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:39.60,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stamp ink is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:43.93,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it only me? Am I the only one who finds this situation strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:47.23,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is carbon paper. Underneath it is the wedding request form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.11,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you for your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:51.11,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Efforts my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:00.41,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.49,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll leave my purse with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:04.54,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It'll spill, so don't tilt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:05.91,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:12.09,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now please enjoy this super exhilarating and horrifying experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.93,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They used an abandoned hospital to build a haunted house, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.60,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It does have the correct atmosphere.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.31,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rather than Himeji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:28.48,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This voice... Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:34.36,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is this, a computer-generated voice? Or is it Hideyoshi imitating me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.53,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever it is, it's not scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:42.74,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Himeji suits me better{} than Shouko; her boobs are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.95,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Himeji suits me better than Shouko; her boobs are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:50.29,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.67,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this what he meant by exhilarating and horrifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.30,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.84,0:12:00.72,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.64,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}God damn it. Even though the theme changed, it's still freaking scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:04.68,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:07.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait! Don't be so rash! This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:12.94,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.52,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So how was it? Want to get married now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How does this have anything to do with marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:19.70,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's well-known that when a man and a woman go through a life-and-death situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.78,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}their relationship becomes stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:25.58,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's only when the woman is not the one threatening the man's life in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.50,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji, it's about time we have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:31.62,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, we've been running around the whole time. I'm hungry as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:41.51,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me guests, I'd like to announce that there's a special lunch at our restaurant today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:49.35,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a special menu prepared for those with premium tickets, so please try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.52,Baka While,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Special menu, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.27,Baka While,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please head towards the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.06,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.81,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong, Shouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:57.48,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm looking forward to the special menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.90,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:03.07,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:05.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anything is good if I eat it with Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:14.00,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, thank you for attending our special lunch show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:20.42,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We actually have a high school couple who are going out{} to get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.30,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.64,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Therefore, we shall be hosting a special event for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:30.68,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's called the Kisaragi Grand Park's Wedding Experience Present Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:35.56,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap, they cut off the escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:39.36,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are a total of five questions. If all of them are answered correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:42.65,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you will receive an extremely extravagant wedding plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:46.45,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you so desire, you can immediately register too! No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.66,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:51.95,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then Sakamoto Yuuji-san and Shouko-san, please head up on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.54,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who the hell's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.62,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wedding Experience... I must work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:59.04,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A dream-like wedding experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:59.04,Baka While,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Calm down, Shouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.88,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shit, I have to think of some way to get out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.43,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.26,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh right! I'll just have to answer them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.35,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I {i}was{/i} once known as the "Prodigy."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.31,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Answering the questions wrong should be a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.85,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}First question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.02,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bastard, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:15.81,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is no question that I don't know the answer to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.94,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When is Sakamoto Yuuji-san and Shouko-san's marriage anniversary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:24.86,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is this? I don't even know what the question means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:25.91,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.57,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Every day is our marriage anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:33.00,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct! Every day is their marriage anniversary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:33.95,Baka While,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop! I can't handle the embarrassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:33.95,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Second question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.87,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn it, I have to answer wrong no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:40.29,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where was their wedding held?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.38,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Miso Mackerel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.84,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:45.76,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:49.01,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Their wedding will be held at the Kisaragi Grand Park's Phoenix Room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:53.43,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}also known as the Miso Mackerel Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.81,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait! You definitely gave it that name just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:57.35,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, to the third question!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:15:00.06,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know what you guys are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:03.28,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll definitely answer the next question wrong, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.61,0:15:05.44,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did the two meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.14,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.28,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This one is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.58,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:12.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:17.29,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll answer half-way through the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.29,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fourth Question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:19.96,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You guys—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.21,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I know the—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.13,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:28.09,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Crap... There's no way I can answer the questions wrong if this continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:29.87,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(300,0)}Sign: End
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it over for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.05,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.72,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were planning on getting married too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:37.89,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do only those two get special treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.23,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let us go up there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.03,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Excuse me, the round is still—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.36,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up, octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:51.45,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm also a customer, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:56.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want to go through a wedding experience too, just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.33,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.50,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop blabbing, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:02.29,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It means we want to participate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.96,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then how about this: we'll ask the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:10.84,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If they answer correctly, it's their win. If not, it's ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.51,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can't just—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:13.72,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.26,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With these idiots,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:18.43,Baka Thought Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can definitely escape from this horrifying wedding experience ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.85,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here's the question, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:26.53,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where is the capital of Europe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.16,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Congratulations! Sakamoto Yuuji-san and Shouko-san won
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:40.93,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}the Kisaragi Grand Park Wedding Experience Present!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:40.93,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sign: Wedding Experience
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:49.09,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll finally be moving onto today's main event: the wedding experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:54.43,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone, please give a warm welcome to the groom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:01.64,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm definitely killing you guys later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.94,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let us introduce the groom to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:08.15,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, never mind. It's just an experience, and it's also a pain to do this. Let's skip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:08.78,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:12.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, here comes the bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.09,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:37.97,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:43.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do I look like a bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:48.19,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right. At least you don't look like a groom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:49.98,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.49,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:53.86,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.99,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:01.04,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's always been my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.25,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since I was a kid, it's been my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:10.30,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}to have a wedding with Yuuji.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:13.80,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Becoming your bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:20.35,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a dream that I thought would never come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So I'm very happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:27.52,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With no one else. Just here, with Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:33.24,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shouko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:37.07,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.62,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's putting me to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:44.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Screw the boring love story;{} hurry up and get to the next part!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:48.25,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We're really busy,{} but we still came, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:50.59,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't need the soap opera crap;{} just show us the good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:55.38,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And really, your dream is to be a bride? How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:57.22,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, it's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.18,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is just a big joke, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.39,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you say, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.19,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How dare you say that to Kirishima-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:10.69,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's take this outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:12.61,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop it, Yoshii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:15.03,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll ruin the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:15.86,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.78,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Calm down, Yoshii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.78,Baka While,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If they keep doing this, Kirishima-san will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:20.03,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.04,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:35.13,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yoshii-kun, you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.26,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's not over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:41.10,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.10,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did Kirishima go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.06,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:45.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.73,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you have any idea where she could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.94,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we don't hurry and find her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:50.65,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry, but I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.36,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's troublesome. Besides, I want to go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:53.98,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.40,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm about to burst, so see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.99,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That wedding sure sucked beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:05.99,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's my dream to be a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.99,0:20:08.33,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How was that? Close, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:12.67,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You sounded just like her! Hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.17,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.09,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastard, you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:19.84,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:24.05,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But lend me your face for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:36.19,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.49,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're late, Shouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.20,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:42.70,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I figured you'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:46.79,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:47.45,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.00,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is my dream weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:54.84,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shouko, I'll just say this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.47,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The feelings you have for me are misplaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:05.18,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seven years ago, I was an idiot,{} and I dragged you in with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:08.14,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just wanted to take responsibility at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:15.02,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've wasted so much time on a good-for-nothing like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.78,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.65,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.49,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't laugh at your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.78,0:21:29.95,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although you've got the wrong person,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.71,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I do think that it's admirable to stay faithful to one person for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:40.13,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So have pride in your dream. It won't lose to anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:45.39,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But only if you don't have the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:52.06,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is from a rare occasion, so take it home as a souvenir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.44,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.23,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, and also!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:22:00.28,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The bento was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:05.70,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go home now, we don't want people to get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:06.74,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:08.70,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:13.66,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't misplace my feelings at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.17,0:23:50.64,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The eighth question. What is the Japanese name for "computer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:52.76,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Choudenjizunou!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:54.76,TL Note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}TL Note: Literally means Super Electrical Brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.76,0:23:54.06,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sounds strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.06,0:23:57.73,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next week: Rampage, Labyrinth, and Summoned Being Custody Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.87,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}These will be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:01.88,Baka Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}
